special_powers.name: MINION: KRYPTON UNITED
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character of a higher point value possessing either the Superman Ally team ability or the Kryptonian keyword is within 8 squares, Kryptonian Soldier can use Willpower.

special_powers.name: MINION: KRYPTON UNITED
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character of a higher point value possessing either the Superman Ally team ability or the Kryptonian keyword is within 8 squares, Kryptonian Infiltrator can use Willpower.

special_powers.name: MINION: THE RELIGION OF CRIME
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character named Bruno Mannheim is within 8 squares, Intergang Underboss can use Toughness.

special_powers.name: 7 DEADLY BROTHERS
special_powers.description: Modify this character's attack value by +1 whenever you control 4 or more characters named "Seven Deadly Brothers."  Instead, modify this character's combat values by +1 whenever you control 7 or more characters named "Seven Deadly Brothers."

special_powers.name: MASS INCREASE
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 4 squares of Star Boy can't be given actions to use Charge, Running Shot, or Hypersonic Speed and halve their speed values when given a move action.

special_powers.name: FORCE FIELD BELT
special_powers.description: Brainiac 5 can use Invulnerability. Give Braniac 5 a free action and choose an adjacent character with the Legion of Super-Heroes keyword. That character can use Toughness until your next turn as long as it is adjacent to Brainiac 5.

special_powers.name: TWELFTH-LEVEL INTELLECT
special_powers.description: Brainiac 5 can use Outwit. Once during your turn Brainiac 5 can use Perplex or Probability Control.

special_powers.name: SNEAKING AROUND THE FORTRESS
special_powers.description: Lois Lane, Superwoman can use Stealth and possesses Earthbound/Neutralized.

special_powers.name: BUST THE GANGS
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose a team ability. Modify Gangbuster's attack value by +1 for each KO'd opposing character possessing that team ability.

special_powers.name: PREVENT THE SHORT
special_powers.description: When there are no squares of water terrain within 8 squares of Livewire, modifiy her damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: ERASED MYSELF FROM YOUR MINDS
special_powers.description: Lines of fire drawn to Maxwell Lord by opposing characters are blocked unless he's taken damage from an opponent's attack this game.

special_powers.name: MINION: PROTECT THE BOSS
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character Lex Luthor is within 8 squares, modify Mercy Graves' attack and speed values by +1 and she can use Defend.

special_powers.name: LAST PERFECT COCKTAIL WAS A SUPER-SERUM
special_powers.description: When turning the dial, if this click is revealed due to damage taken from a opponent's attack, stop turning the dial.

special_powers.name: REIGN OF THE SUPERMEN
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Superman has been KO'd this game, modify Superboy's combat values by +1 for the rest of the game.

special_powers.name: REIGN OF THE SUPERMEN
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Superman has been KO'd this game, modify Steel's combat values by +1 for the rest of the game.

special_powers.name: HAMMER DOWN
special_powers.description: When Steel attacks a character with 2 action tokens, you may choose to modify his attack value by +2 or his damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: CHARISMATIC CRIMINAL
special_powers.description: Bruno Mannheim can use Mind Control, but only targeting characters of 50 points or less.

special_powers.name: THREE STORIES TALL
special_powers.description: Bruno Mannheim possesses the Giant damage symbol.

special_powers.name: THE HUMAN TARGET
special_powers.description: Friendly characters adjacent to Human Target may use Shape Change if they cannot already. If a friendly adjacent character makes a successful Shape Change roll, Human Target becomes the target of that attack, even if he is otherwise an illegal target.

special_powers.name: RADIANT SPECTRUM
special_powers.description: Sun Boy can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast and Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: ABSORBANCY
special_powers.description: Give Earth Man a free action and choose a standard attack power that an adjacent character can use.  Until your next turn, he can use that power.

special_powers.name: NO PLACE TO HIDE, ALIEN!
special_powers.description: Opposing characters with the Cosmic keyword can't be given power actions to use standard Speed powers.  Those characters modify their defense values by -2 when attacked by Earth Man.

special_powers.name: FULL INVISIBILITY
special_powers.description: Invisible Kid can use Stealth. Any line of fire drawn to Invisible Kid is blocked if he has no action tokens.

special_powers.name: SHARED INVISIBILITY
special_powers.description: Give Invisible Kid a free action and choose an adjacent character with the Legion of Super-Heroes keyword. That character can use Stealth until your next turn as long as it is adjacent to Invisible Kid.

special_powers.name: MATTER, EATEN
special_powers.description: Give Matter-Eater Lad a free action and destroy an adjacent wall, adjacent square of blocking terrain, or remove an object in his square or an adjacent square from the game.

special_powers.name: POWER DRAIN
special_powers.description: Parasite can use Outwit, but must also be within 5 squares of the target. If he counters a standard power except Outwit, he can use that standard power and replaces his range value with the targeted character's printed range value until your next turn.

special_powers.name: KILLING IS THE ONLY OPTION
special_powers.description: When an opposing character is KO'd, you may remove an action token from Manchester Black. If the KO'd character was 100 or more points, heal Manchester Black of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: RUTHLESS TELEKINETIC
special_powers.description: Manchester Black can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast and Telekinesis.

special_powers.name: WAIL OF THE BANSHEE
special_powers.description: Silver Banshee can use Incapacitate as if she possesses "3 targets". When she uses it, after actions resolve deal damage to each hit character equal to the number of action tokens on them.

special_powers.name: MINION: KILL THE BOSS'S ENEMIES
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character named Lex Luthor is within 8 squares, modify Hope Taya's attack and speed values by +1.

special_powers.name: LOBOTOMIZED STRONGMAN
special_powers.description: Non can use Super Strength. In addition to the normal effects, when using an object during an attack, increase the damage dealt by 1.

special_powers.name: LEARNING TO SEE THE LIGHT
special_powers.description: Project: Superman possesses a range value equal to his click number.

special_powers.name: REIGN OF THE SUPERMEN
special_powers.description: If a friendly character named Superman has been KO'd this game, modify Eradicator's combat values by +1 for the rest of the game.

special_powers.name: KRYPTONIAN CLONE, COMPUTER MIND
special_powers.description: Eradicator can use Super Senses and Toughness.

special_powers.name: MENTAL BACKUP
special_powers.description: Give Cyborg Superman a free action and remove an object (held or not) within 6 squares from the map. Roll a d6 and heal Cyborg Superman equal to the half of that d6 roll.

special_powers.name: TOTAL MACHINE CONTROL
special_powers.description: Give Cyborg Superman a free action to use Telekinesis, but only to move an object or attack with an object.

special_powers.name: EXCESSIVE FORCE
special_powers.description: Once per turn, when Magog KO's an opposing character, after actions resolve Magog may take one action as a free action.

special_powers.name: A TEACHER AND HEALER, IN THE END
special_powers.description: Magog can use Support. When he does, the targeted character's defense value becomes Magog's unmodified defense value. Before any attack roll, Magog may replace his defense value with the unmodified defense value of an adjacent friendly character.

special_powers.name: DON'T BELONG
special_powers.description: If he begins on his yellow 80 point line, Composite Superman's team abilities are Uncopyable.

special_powers.name: PROPHETIC MANIPULATION
special_powers.description: At the end of your turn, as a free action you may choose an opposing character and a friendly character, both within 8 squares of Libra.  When that opposing character attacks that friendly character before your next turn, you may have that attack roll be rerolled once per turn.

special_powers.name: UNITING LEADER
special_powers.description: If Libra is the highest point friendly character on the map, modify his attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: ILLUSIONARY WALL
special_powers.description: Princess Projectra can use Barrier as if she possessed a range value of 4.

special_powers.name: FULL ILLUSIONS
special_powers.description: Give Princess Projectra a free action and choose an adjacent character with the Legion of Super Heroes keyword.  That character can use Super Senses until your next turn as long as it is adjacent to Princess Projectra.

special_powers.name: FREE ENERGY FORM
special_powers.description: Wildfire can use Poison and Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: WILD ENERGY ABSORPTION
special_powers.description: After one of Wildfire's ranged combat actions resolves, heal him of one damage for each opposing character that took damage during that action.

special_powers.name: CHECKMATE IS A LAW UNTO ITSELF
special_powers.description: Characters with the Checkmate keyword can use the Police team ability as long as they are adjacent to Maxwell Lord.

special_powers.name: CONTROL SUPERMAN
special_powers.description: Maxwell Lord can use Mind Control, but you may assign a hit target two actions as free actions instead of one. One of the two must be a move action.

special_powers.name: MAP OF THE MULTIVERSE
special_powers.description: Starman can use Phasing/Teleport. Opposing characters adjacent to Starman modify their attack value by -1 if he used Phasing/Teleport during your previous turn.

special_powers.name: BLAH HEALING FACTOR BLAH
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, as a free action you may heal Lobo of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: LAZY DAWG
special_powers.description: Lobo can use Flurry. Before the second attack, roll a d6. His damage value becomes the result minus 1 and is locked.

special_powers.name: HOOK, LINE, AND MASSACRE
special_powers.description: Give Lobo a power action, and choose an opposing character within 5 squares and line of fire, and roll a d6. If the d6 result is higher than the number of squares to that character, you may place that character in a square adjacent to Lobo. On any result, you may then make a close combat attack.

special_powers.name: RELENTLESS, UNSTOPPABLE
special_powers.description: Doomsday uses Battle Fury and can't be placed by Telekinesis.

special_powers.name: STEADY COURSE TO METROPOLIS
special_powers.description: Doomsday can use Charge.  When using Charge, he ignores other characters and terrain for movement purposes except walls and indoor blocking terrain.

special_powers.name: FINAL CONFRONTATION
special_powers.description: If an opponent controls only one character, you may give Doomsday a power action.  Place Doomsday next to that character and make a close combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: X-RAY VISION
special_powers.description: Ursa ignores hindering terrain for line of fire purposes when making attacks.

special_powers.name: KRYPTONIAN BLACK OPS
special_powers.description: Ursa can use Running Shot and Stealth.

special_powers.name: LIGHT SENSITIVE
special_powers.description: If Ursa occupies hindering terrain, modify her attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: MERA'S HELMET
special_powers.description: Wonder Woman can't be the target of Incapacitate, Mind Control, or Penetrating/Psychic Blast. Opposing characters possessing the "dolphin speed symbol" or "transporter dolphin speed symbol" possess Battle Fury.

special_powers.name: DIVIDE AND CONQUER
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 8 squares that are not adjacent to another opposing character modify their defense values by -1 when targeted by a close combat attack. Friendly characters within 8 squares that are adjacent to another friendly character modify their attack values by +1 when making close combat attacks.

special_powers.name: I'LL SHOW YOU YOUNG PUNKS HOW IT'S DONE
special_powers.description: The Bat-Man modifies his attack value by +1 when he's attacking a character whose current click number is lower than The Bat-Man's current click number.

special_powers.name: THE HOUSE ALWAYS WINS
special_powers.description: Immediately before The Bat-Man makes an attack roll, you may choose a number between 1 and 6.  If the attack hits and the chosen number is on one die, modify his damage value by +1.  If the attack hits and chosen number is on both dice, instead modify his damage value by +2, and after actions resolve, heal The Bat-Man of 2 damage.

special_powers.name: SUDDEN STOP
special_powers.description: After an action resolves in which The Flash moved due to his own action, you may place a hindering terrain marker in an adjacent square of clear terrain and an opposing character occupying that square may be knocked back from The Flash 1 square.

special_powers.name: TIME JUMP
special_powers.description: Give The Flash a power action if he began the game on your force, and remove him from the map after resolving that action. At the beginning of your next turn, you may place The Flash (with no action tokens) anywhere on the map if you control another character. If all other characters on The Flash's force are KO'd while he is removed from the map, he is KO'd. He can't use this power again until he's taken damage from an opponent's attack.

special_powers.name: FLOOD THE LAND IN REVENGE
special_powers.description: When Aquaman is KO'd, all grounded terrain becomes squares of water terrain for the rest of the game instead of squares of clear, hindering, or blocking terrain, even though this character is not on the map.

special_powers.name: INVADE THE SURFACE
special_powers.description: After an action resolves in which Aquaman moves due to his own action, you may give any number of other friendly characters possessing "dolphin speed symbol" or "transporter dolphin speed symbol" a free action to move up to three squares if they currently occupy water terrain.

special_powers.name: UNDERGROUND GEYSER
special_powers.description: Give Aquaman a double power action and choose any square of clear terrain within a range of 8 and line of fire. Place a special terrain marker in the chosen square and it becomes water terrain for the rest of the game. Deal a character occupying that square 3 damage, and then each character occupying an adjacent square is knocked back from the chosen square 3 squares.

special_powers.name: ALL MUST BE SUBMERGED
special_powers.description: Aquaman can use Toughness and Willpower.

special_powers.name: IMPRISONED IN SOMETHING ORDINARY
special_powers.description: When the Queen of Fables is hit by a character's attack using a standard object, deal her 1 unavoidable damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: I'M THE HERO OF THIS TALE
special_powers.description: Queen of Fables can use Willpower. When she attacks an opposing character, she may replace her attack and damage values with the printed attack and damage values of the target +1.

special_powers.name: REWRITE THE STORY
special_powers.description: Queen of Fables can use Perplex and Probability Control.

special_powers.name: PLANETARY DESTRUCTION
special_powers.description: When you reveal your force, you may place 3 "DRILL" special terrain markers on the map outside of starting areas. At the beginning of your turn, as a free action, you may deal 1 penetrating damage to each character occupying a square containing one of these markers. At the end of your turn as a free action you may place each of these markers into a square adjacent to its current square that doesn't contain another "DRILL" special terrain marker. When Imperiex is KO'd, remove these markers from the map.

special_powers.name: SUMMON THE HOLLOWERS
special_powers.description: Give Imperiex a double power action. You may place any of Imperiex's "DRILL" special terrain markers in different squares adjacent to Imperiex.

special_powers.name: ENTROPY UNLEASHED
special_powers.description: Imperiex can use Energy Explosion as if he has 3 lightning bolts, Incapacitate as if he has 2 lightning bolts, and Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: OUT OF THE GREEN
special_powers.description: Before being given a move or close combat action, you may place Swamp Thing in any square of printed hindering terrain within 4 squares.

special_powers.name: HALLUCINATORY TOXINS
special_powers.description: Swamp Thing can use Poison. When he does, a character that takes damage and has zero action tokens is given an action token.

special_powers.name: NATURE'S ASSAULT
special_powers.description: Give Swamp Thing a free action and choose any number of characters occupying a square of printed hindering terrain within 4 squares. Deal 1 damage to the chosen characters.

special_powers.name: STONY LORD OF APOKOLIPS
special_powers.description: Each time penetrating damage would be dealt to Darkseid, he may ignore 1 of that penetrating damage. If he does so, he can't transfer the damage.

special_powers.name: BOOM TUBE INVASION
special_powers.description: Darkseid can use Phasing/Teleport. When he does, he can use the Carry ability to carry up to 3 characters regardless of their speed symbols. One character of 125 points or less that shares a keyword with Darkseid and was carried by him this turn may be given a non-free action.

special_powers.name: DEFEND NEW KRYPTON MY WAY
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters and other friendly characters that possess the Phantom Zone keyword modify their attack values by +1.

special_powers.name: KNEEL BEFORE ZOD!
special_powers.description: Give Zod a power action. The controller of each opposing character within 2 squares with 0 or 1 action tokens can choose to give that character an action token. Each opposing character within 2 squares that was not given an action token is dealt 2 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: THE MOST DANGEROUS KRYPTONIAN ALIVE!
special_powers.description: If an opposing character possesses the Superman Ally team ability, friendly characters can't use the Superman Enemy team ability; instead if there are two or more friendly characters possessing the Superman Enemy team ability on the map, they can each use Outwit.

special_powers.name: DEFENDER OF KHANDAQ
special_powers.description: Black Adam can use Impervious, but if he would be dealt 4 or more damage, he reduces that damage by 3 instead of 2. His powers and abilities can't be countered except for his Outwit.

special_powers.name: LIGHTNING REGENERATION
special_powers.description: Black Adam can use Regeneration. If he uses it and heals, after actions resolve deal 1 penetrating damage to each opposing character within 2 squares.

special_powers.name: HELL IS HERE!
special_powers.description: Black Adam can use Charge. He can use it normally, or he can be given a double power action to use Charge with a locked speed value of 10 if he doesn't use the Carry ability or Super Strength.

special_powers.name: WORLD WAR III
special_powers.description: Friendly characters named Osiris modify their attack values +1 if they are not on their starting click. Friendly characters named Isis modify their defense values +1 if they are not on their starting click.

special_powers.name: A PIECE OF MY SHIP
special_powers.description: Superman can use Super Strength. When Superman uses an object in an attack, he deals penetrating damage. When you place your force on the map at the beginning of the game, Superman begins holding a standard heavy object. (This doesn't count against your object limit.)

special_powers.name: THE APOCALYPSE DAWNS WITH ME
special_powers.description: When a character takes damage from Superman's attack, that character modifies its defense value by -1 and damage dealt to that character is increased by 1 until the end of the turn.

special_powers.name: SUPERMAN RETURNED!
special_powers.description: Once per game, when Superman would be KO'd, instead heal him to click #6 and modify his combat values by +1 for the rest of the game. When this happens, he counts as KO'd for traits named "Reign of the Supermen".

special_powers.name: KRYPTONIAN KNOWLEDGE CRYSTALS
special_powers.description: Superman can use Perplex, but only to target himself.

special_powers.name: BLACKSMITH'S APPRENTICE
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters that possess the Armor keyword modify their defense values by +1.

special_powers.name: THERE'S NO ONE ELSE WHO CAN END THIS
special_powers.description: If Kal is the only character on your force, modify his combat values by +1.

special_powers.name: STARMETAL ARMOR
special_powers.description: Kal can use Impervious. Once per game, after Kal is dealt damage but before he takes it, you may instead give him an action token and ignore that damage. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: MINION: FOLLOW OR REBEL
special_powers.description: Whenever a friendly character with a higher point value and possessing the Superman Ally or Superman Enemy Team Ability is within 8 squares, Superman Robot can use that team ability.

special_powers.name: DEFEND NEW KRYPTON MY WAY
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters possessing the Kryptonian keyword or the Superman Ally team ability modify their defense values by +1.

special_powers.name: LEADER OF THE MANHUNTERS
special_powers.description: After Manhunter Grandmaster resolves a non-free action, you may give any number of other friendly characters with the Robot keyword a free action to move 1 square. If those characters are also named Manhunter, they may move 3 squares instead.

special_powers.name: BUT I WANT TO DIE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, Manhunter Grandmaster uses Regeneration as a free action, but can't otherwise use it through this power.

special_powers.name: ROCK-BREATH
special_powers.description: Bizarro-Girl can use Incapacitate.  When she does, a hit character's speed powers are countered until your next turn.

special_powers.name: ME AM SO SCARED
special_powers.description: If Bizarro-Girl didn't take any damage since your last turn, she can use Willpower.

special_powers.name: ESCAPE FROM THE UNDERVERSE
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters that can use the Flight ability modify their speed values by +2 when they are given a move action.

special_powers.name: PHANTOM ZONE PROJECTOR
special_powers.description: Give Superman Beyond a power action and make a close or ranged combat attack that deals no damage. If it hits, you may place the hit character in any starting area used this game and then deal that character 1 penetrating damage.

Characters within 4 squares modify their attack values by -1 and can't use the Flight ability. Characters within 4 squares that possess the Superman Ally team ability or the Kryptonian Keyword can't have damage dealt to them reduced below 1.

Characters within 4 squares must roll a d6 immediately before they are given a non-free action. On a roll of 1-2, the character is given a power action to do nothing instead, but can use Perplex until your next turn if they can't already use it.

Characters within 4 squares can use Mind Control and Smoke Cloud if they can't already. Characters using Mind Control in this way can only target characters of a lower point value. All characters within 4 squares using Mind Control and Smoke Cloud have a minimum range value of 6 when using those powers.
Characters within 4 squares can't use Exploit Weakness, Penetrating/Psychic Blast, Pulse Wave, or Telekinesis. A character holding this object can't use any powers except Super Strength.
Other squares within 4 squares become clear terrain instead of hindering terrain. This has no effect on objects or water terrain.
Characters within 4 squares that are 75 points or less can use the Flight ability for as long as they are within 4 squares.
